<HEADLINE> AP Names Marquez To Calif. Post  </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
   SAN FRANCISCO (AP) -- Anthony Marquez, Bay Area editor of the San
Jose Mercury News, has returned to The Associated Press as
assistant chief of bureau for Northern California and Northern
Nevada.
</P>
<P>
   Marquez will supervise news, photos and administration for AP
bureaus in San Francisco, San Jose, Berkeley, Sacramento and
