</P>
<P>
   Lionel faces a first-degree murder charge for the July death of
Tiffany Eunick. No trial date has been set.
</P>
<P>
   The lawyer said he chose Johnson because he lives in South
Florida.
</P>
<P>
   Johnson was traveling and was unavailable for comment. A
spokesman for the World Wrestling Federation said the group was
unaware of the subpoena and had no comment.
</P>
